description: There is little doubt Jackie Moore is an equal opportunity employer when it comes to which hole she likes filled. We took her out to a friend's boat and tried our best to keep up with her. We finally got to use the very noisy "Pussy Whacker", a machine we got from Ken's Twisted Mind a long time ago, but were never able to use because it's a fume spewing 2-stroke engine.
title: Jackie Moore
